data.description: Beautifully Remodeled 4-Bedroom Home in Bloomingdale, GA! Discover the charm and comfort of this recently remodeled home on a spacious .93-acre lot:  Stylish Remodel: Recently remodeled to offer a fresh and modern appeal. Generous Bedrooms: Featuring 4 bedrooms for ample living space. Modern Bathrooms: Enjoy the convenience of 2 full bathrooms, elegantly designed.  Expansive Lot: Situated on a spacious .93-acre lot, providing room for outdoor activities like hanging out by a firepit on these chilly South Ga. This large yard also offers the possibility for potential expansion. Tranquil Bloomingdale Setting: Experience the serenity of living in Bloomingdale, GA, with its charming community and natural surroundings. Only a few minutes to the beach. Outdoor Oasis: Boasts a nice new 12x24 shed in the backyard, creating a perfect space for storage or a nice she shed/ Man cave to unwind and watch the football game. For More Information: Call now to inquire about this delightful 4-bedroom home in Bloomingdale, GA. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!  #HomeForSale #BloomingdaleGA #RemodeledHome #RealEstateOpportunity #OutdoorLiving Call Victoria A Arthur today to set up your showing! 706-526-8171
